{"tid":1641650,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【新港城保安事件】想救全港保安嘅入嚟！！","createTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:34:02.000Z","uid":70786,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a635ff98608112c4a6a068766e742c805c3eef","tid":1641650,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"對於保安最緊要係咩呀？大利是呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要對抗黑警高調拉人低調放人所製造嘅白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係搞個香港最佳保安獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由各界人士籌集獎金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n表揚盡力保護香港市民嘅保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邀請傳媒朋友大搞特搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到好似外國彩票派彩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/105869500-1556123052651manuelcheckcindybarca.jpg?v=1556123272&amp;w=1400&amp;h=950\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cnbcfm.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fimage%2F105869500-1556123052651manuelcheckcindybarca.jpg%3Fv%3D1556123272%26w%3D1400%26h%3D950&h=7f2caa24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保安得獎示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整個特大利是封入特大銀碼支票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再由傳媒見證下開封<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大頭影住佢中獎個興奮樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁做俾全港保安見到，話鳩知黑警拉唔拉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要有封大利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搏埋條命都要保護私人地方內嘅民眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一屆獎金暫定五注中，由新港城五名被捕保安瓜分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警想同香港人玩白色恐怖？香港人就同你玩PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2550783f0106134362bc839a7f4b7401c314613e","tid":1641650,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"新港城保安被捕，最佳處理方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641567</a>"},{"pid":"4b8db4b00367f1efa247008684c2493e468ef80d","tid":1641650,"uid":182827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:57:03.000Z","msg":"可能會俾人話收利益wo<br />\n保安可能有自己行業既操守要遵守"},{"pid":"a1944b0265d602cccb668d625507a1bfc907f289","tid":1641650,"uid":154702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"要推<br />\n<br />\n個垃圾的士司機有52 萬<br />\n都係玩緊呢套稿賞邏輯"},{"pid":"5494de138468b734b30ef24a196a005d36710247","tid":1641650,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8db4b00367f1efa247008684c2493e468ef80d","tid":1641650,"uid":182827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:57:03.000Z","msg":"可能會俾人話收利益wo<br />\n保安可能有自己行業既操守要遵守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"平時利是就可以收？<br />\n有冇人知行規有咩灰色地帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1372008c41de4806c689b02b5db82989b9ab13","tid":1641650,"uid":34400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8db4b00367f1efa247008684c2493e468ef80d","tid":1641650,"uid":182827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:57:03.000Z","msg":"可能會俾人話收利益wo<br />\n保安可能有自己行業既操守要遵守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n放心"},{"pid":"1e5c767bfef14853c15c06a001acbfe18dde80ce","tid":1641650,"uid":134161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8db4b00367f1efa247008684c2493e468ef80d","tid":1641650,"uid":182827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-0